messages.message: Hi folks, we’re in the process of migrating our marketing website right now. Its currently been deployed in dogfood, however there are some config changes that we still need to make. You might notice some bad links, but please ignore for now. Prod should be synced with the new dogfood site sometime in the next few weeks once we work through all of the issues.
In the meantime, if you need to login you can directly go to https://dogfood.instabase.com/account/login
_Crosses fingers that ‘migrating marketing’ means/includes moving it off it’s own GKE cluster_
No its still the same setup :thisisfine:
